						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Broken pillar in front of the Kalmēśvara Temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>Indra III—A.D. 920-21.</p>						

						<p>The record refers to the year <hi rend="bold">Vikrama</hi> which probably is the one that fell in Indra III's reign and which coincided with <hi rend="bold">A.D. 920-21.</hi></p>						

						<p>This record refers to the reign of Indraballala and states that in the cyclic year Vikrama, Saḍagarara Tiḻtamma made a gift of <hi rend="italic">gōsahasra.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
